title: Young Avengers Complete (2005 - 2012) All Appearances All Series
description:
This torrent contains all the appearances of the Young Avengers across the whole Marvel Universe between 2005 and 2012.

Reading order:

Young Avengers Volume 1 (2005)
Civil War (2006)
She Hulk Volume 2 (2008)
Young Avengers Presents (2008)
Secret Invasion (2008)
What If, (2008)
Dark Reign (2009)
Siege (2010)
Avengers: Children's Crusade (2010-2012)
